One Voice: The Greatest Clips is a DVD release by Australian singer John Farnham. The DVD was released in Australia on 20 October 2003 in conjunction with a 2 disc greatest hits compilation titled, One Voice: The Greatest Hits. This DVD contains all of John Farnham's music videos and clips from 1966-2003.
